Episode 9

3
00:00:52,109 --> 00:00:54,143
[What's the point of being an immortal]

4
00:00:59,060 --> 00:01:00,293
Elder, why did you pay

5
00:01:00,294 --> 00:01:01,528
such great respect earlier

6
00:01:02,063 --> 00:01:04,631
Please forgive me for not
recognizing a great man when I see one

7
00:01:04,632 --> 00:01:05,932
I was disrespectful to you, Lord

8
00:01:05,933 --> 00:01:08,168
and I hope you can forgive my offense

9
00:01:08,169 --> 00:01:10,170
He turns out to be an important figure

10
00:01:10,571 --> 00:01:12,539
