Lord Jiuming also made a point to instruct me

203
00:09:35,309 --> 00:09:36,209
Not to reveal his identity

204
00:09:37,411 --> 00:09:38,377
Thinking back now

205
00:09:39,012 --> 00:09:40,480
It does seem quite peculiar

206
00:09:43,584 --> 00:09:44,984
Now that you mention it

207
00:09:45,419 --> 00:09:47,353
I am indeed quite interested in this

208
00:09:47,354 --> 00:09:50,056
Immortal Physician Little Isatis

209
00:09:51,191 --> 00:09:51,958
Prepare the sedan chair

210
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,026
to Herb Hall

211
00:09:54,495 --> 00:09:54,994
Yes
